MTK native video color converter

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
Convert video dumped frames to YUV420 color format.
Support input format: MTKYUV, Android YV12 and ARGB8888.

HOW TO USE IT?
==============
1. The executable bin file - mtkvfc, which is put in /system/xbin,
   is automatically generated after system boot.
2. Type mtkvfc at command line to show the usages.
3. Converted file - output.yuv will be put in /mnt/sdcard.
